data.description: Looking for a ton of space for the family? This beautiful home offers a total of 3458 sq ft. On the main floor, you find 3 bed, 2 bath, a gallery kitchen with breakfast area, dining, formal living and also a large family room with a fireplace. The basement offers 2 extra rooms (that could be used as bedrooms, game rooms, arts & crafts, etc), a full bath, a 2nd den with fireplace alongside a small kitchenette. You will have a covered back patio overlooking a fenced backyard for all your get togethers.  There is also 2 car attached garage and a 2 car detached garage. Home has a metal roof, new fridge, new dishwasher, new Hvac 2021, hot water heater, are waiting for you. Pool DOES NOT convey. Call today for your private showing.
